{"word":"G5274 - ὑπολαμβάνω - hypolambánō - hoop-ol-am-ban'-o - Answer","slug":"G5274","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπολαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hypolambánō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-ol-am-ban'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Answer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B2;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - hupolambano&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-ol-am-ban'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>; to <i>take</i> from <i>below</i>, that is, <i>carry upward</i>; figuratively to <i>take up</i>, that is, <i>continue</i> a discourse or topic; mentally to <i>assume</i> (<i>presume</i>): - answer, receive, suppose."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356\">G4356</a>"}]}